    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''Lazio Opens Race With an Attack on Mrs. Clinton'' (front page, May 21):</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''Lazio Opens Race With an Attack on Mrs. Clinton'' (front page, May 21):</p>
        <p>''I think her ambition is the issue,'' Representative Rick Lazio declared of Hillary Rodham Clinton as he announced his candidacy for senator from New York -- less than 24 hours after Mayor Rudolph W. Giuliani withdrew from the race. Whose ambition is the issue?</p>
        <p>MIKE KELLY  Redmond, Wash., May 21, 2000</p>
      </block>
